I built something similar for my latest webapp to validate json-requests in python, the syntax is like this:<p><pre><code>    {
        &quot;content&quot;: Required(str),
        &quot;username&quot;: Required(str, validate=username_is_ok, transform=lambda x: x.lower(), 
                   fail_message=&quot;Username isn&#x27;t valid&quot;),
        &quot;message&quot;: Optional(str),
        &quot;some_list&quot;: Required({
            &quot;name&quot;: Required(str),
            &quot;date&quot;: Required(str)
        }, is_list=True)
    }
</code></pre>
Then I can provide this in a hook to the request method.

